title: THIS 2BR/2BA APARTMENT HAS A WALK-IN CLOSET!
posting_body: ['Canyon Ridge at Napa Junction', 'CALL US TODAY!', 'show contact info', 'x142', 'Want more information?', '<URL>', 'show contact info', '/floorplan/3772334/1?extnId=9612391', '2 \xa0bedroom 2 bath 1102Sq.', 'Ft.  $3,379 - $3,548/mo', '* Unit 310 - Available 09/08/22', 'Find the perfect home at Canyon Ridge.', 'Indulge in comfort and style at Canyon Ridge.', 'Welcome home to this expansive two-bedroom, two-bathroom apartment at Canyon Ridge!', 'There is plenty of space to spread out and relax thanks to the spacious floor plan that includes a separate dining area!', 'The comfortable bedrooms feature ample storage space, including a walk-in closet in the master bedroom, where you can easily organize all of your wardrobe items and accessories!', 'Inside the designer kitchen, you can prepare meals effortlessly with the stylish appliances and quartz countertops!', 'After a long day, you can unwind on your own private balcony!', 'This luxurious community also offers an extensive collection of amenities for residents to enjoy!', 'You can take advantage of the resort-style saltwater pool, a four-thousand-square-foot clubhouse, and a state-of-the-art fitness center!', 'Stop by Canyon Ridge soon, and ask for more information about this incredible community!', 'FLOORPLAN/UNIT AMENITIES:', '* Garage', '* Storage Space', '* Designer Finishes', '*', 'Pool view', '* Stainless steel appliances', '* Washer Dryer', '* Upgraded Plank Flooring', '* Quartz Countertops', '* First Floor', 'PROPERTY AMENITIES:', '* Playground', '* Spa', '* Fitness Center', '* High Speed Internet Available', '* Clubhouse', '* Covered Parking', '* Conference Room', '* Regular-sized pool', '* Community gas grill/BBQ area', '* Sports court (outside)', '* Large fitness center', '* Separate game room', 'MANAGED BY:', 'Reliant Property Management', 'CALL US TODAY!', 'show contact info', 'x142', 'Address:', '800 Reliant Way American Canyon, CA 94503', 'Equal Housing Opportunity']
